LABEL: 0x76
JPN: 「こちらで水泳教室が開かれていると聞いて」
ENG: "I heard they were holding swimming lessons here?"

LABEL: 0xe6
JPN: 「うちの子も、お願いできますか」
ENG: "I don't suppose you'd coach my child, too?"

LABEL: 0x206
ENG: "How did we end up in a class with a bunch of kids?"

LABEL: 0x2bc
ENG: "You don't look too out of place, though, Nomiki."

LABEL: 0x354
JPN: 「ねぇねぇ、おにーちゃん、あの中の誰と付き合ってるの」
ENG: "Hey, hey, mister! Which of those girls are you going out with?"

LABEL: 0x402
ENG: "I'm so sorry! She's such a handful."

LABEL: 0x438
JPN: 「このおにーちゃんは女の子に興味ない人だよ」
ENG: "He's one of those boys who's not into girls!"

LABEL: 0x4a4
JPN: 「この前、あのおにーちゃんと裸で２人きりで森にいるの見たよ」
ENG: "I saw him naked in the forest with that other boy over there the other day!"

LABEL: 0x524
JPN: 「２人きりじゃなかっただろう」
ENG: "You're making it sound like we were alone!"

LABEL: 0x55c
JPN: 「すいません……この子ったら。こっちきなさい」
ENG: "I-I'm so sorry! She just doesn't listen. Come on, this way."

LABEL: 0x730
JPN: 「は、なんで私は一緒になって無邪気に返事をしているんだ」
ENG: "Wait! Why am I acting like one of the kids!?"

LABEL: 0x792
JPN: と、１人プールからあがってこない。
ENG: One person, however, remained in the pool.

LABEL: 0x9fc
JPN: なんとかプールサイドにあがると、ふらふらと向こうに行ってしまう。
ENG: She pulled herself out of the pool with some difficulty and sort of staggered away from it.

LABEL: 0xa4c
ENG: "Hey, you okay? Are you getting heatstroke, or something?"

LABEL: 0xb56
JPN: 「もうプールに近寄っちゃだめ」
ENG: "You can't go near the pool anymore."

LABEL: 0xbd2
JPN: 「終わりにしたほうがいいよ」

LABEL: 0xcd2
ENG: "Is something going to happen in the pool?"

LABEL: 0xdb4
JPN: 「だから、今、プールに近寄っちゃだめ」
ENG: "So you can't go near the pool for now."

LABEL: 0xe7e
JPN: 「でも皆に、説明のしようがないし」
ENG: "How would I explain it to everyone, though?"

LABEL: 0xeba
JPN: 「子供達も楽しんでるからな」
ENG: "The kids look like they're really having fun, too."

LABEL: 0xf2c
JPN: 「先日もそうやって、何か見えたみたいだけど」
ENG: "You saw something like this the other day too, right?"

LABEL: 0xf72
ENG: "And everything turned out just fine, didn't it?"

LABEL: 0x1014
JPN: 実際は少しだけ不安だった。
ENG: In complete honesty, I was a little nervous.

LABEL: 0x103e
JPN: けど、ここでしろはの言う通り、プールから離れたらなんだか負けな気がした。
ENG: But somehow, I felt like I'd be admitting defeat if I ran away from the pool like she wanted me to.

LABEL: 0x1096
JPN: しろはが言う、妙な予知。
ENG: Shiroha was plagued by her strange premonitions.

LABEL: 0x10be
JPN: そんなもの気にする必要はないって、示したかった。
ENG: But I wanted to show her that they were nothing to fear.

LABEL: 0x10fe
JPN: しろはが何を見たか知らないが、いくらなんでも小学校のプールで溺れるとも思えなかった。
ENG: I didn't know what exactly she'd seen, but I couldn't possibly imagine myself drowning in an elementary school pool.

LABEL: 0x11a4
JPN: プールの中で数人の男の子が遊んでいる。
ENG: There were a couple boys playing around in the pool.

LABEL: 0x11da
ENG: "Hey, didn't you hear me? It's break time!"

LABEL: 0x1236
ENG: They weren't listening in the slightest.

LABEL: 0x1376
JPN: プールサイドの子供も、はしゃぎ出す。
ENG: The kids beside the pool were getting worked up, too.

LABEL: 0x13aa
JPN: 俺はプールに入り、子供達を追いかける。
ENG: I, meanwhile, did my best to chase them down.

LABEL: 0x1556
JPN: 頭上からざわめきが降ってくる。

LABEL: 0x1584
JPN: 歓声が、ざわめきに変わっていく。
ENG: Cheers, blending together into formless static.

LABEL: 0x164e
ENG: What the hell are you doing!?

LABEL: 0x1756
JPN: 手足がばらばらになる感覚。
ENG: I felt my control of my limbs slipping away from me.

LABEL: 0x1780
JPN: そう、あの時、俺は水の中でバラバラになったんだ。
ENG: That's right. Back then, I completely fell apart in the water.

LABEL: 0x17c0
JPN: ばらばらになって……今もまだ、ばらばらだ。
ENG: I fell apart... and even now, I'm still in pieces.

LABEL: 0x1a26
JPN: 俺はなにをしていたんだっけ。
ENG: What was I doing just now?

LABEL: 0x1a52
ENG: I wasn't really doing anything at all.

LABEL: 0x1a76
JPN: ただ、漫然と、時間をつぶしていたんだっけ。
ENG: I was just aimlessly killing time, wasn't I?

LABEL: 0x1ad2
ENG: I really want to go somewhere.

LABEL: 0x1af6
JPN: ここ以外ならどこでもいい。
ENG: Anywhere is fine. Anywhere but here.

LABEL: 0x1b82
JPN: 夏休みも、こうやって過ごすんだろうか。
ENG: I'll probably spend my summer like this, too.

LABEL: 0x1bb8
JPN: あるいはこれからの人生そのものが。
ENG: Maybe even the rest of my life.

LABEL: 0x1bea
JPN: こんな感じ、なのかもしれないな。
ENG: Maybe I'll be like this forever.

LABEL: 0x1c58
ENG: There was a guy standing in front of me.

LABEL: 0x1c78
JPN: 脱色した髪を長くのばした、やたらと図体のでかい男だ。
ENG: His hair was long, messy, and bleached, and he was built pretty large.

LABEL: 0x1cbc
JPN: 見た目は怖いが、案外、のんきな奴だ。
ENG: He looked scary, but was actually a pretty laid-back guy.

LABEL: 0x1e86
JPN: ふと思う、もし……この先に嫌なことが待っていると分かれば。
ENG: A thought struck me out of nowhere.

LABEL: 0x1ed0
JPN: 人は回避することができるのかな。
ENG: If you know that something terrible is waiting for you in the near future, is it possible to avoid it instead?

LABEL: 0x1f00
JPN: きっと、そんなの無理だ。

LABEL: 0x1f28
JPN: それが証拠に、これから何が起こるか分かっているのに、俺は……抗えない。
ENG: Just look at me. I knew what was going to happen, but there was nothing I could do to stop it in spite of that.

LABEL: 0x1f7e
JPN: 結局、引き寄せられて、引きずり込まれていくだけなのかもしれない。
ENG: Maybe fate's just been dragging me along this entire time.

LABEL: 0x1fce
JPN: 運命ってそういうものなんだ。
ENG: Maybe that's just how fate works.

LABEL: 0x1ffa
JPN: 海に現れた、大きな渦みたいに。逃れられない。
ENG: It's like a massive whirlpool in the middle of the ocean. There's no escaping it.

LABEL: 0x2060
JPN: 誰かが必死に呼び止める。
ENG: Someone was desperately trying to stop me.

LABEL: 0x2088
ENG: "Then where am I supposed to go?"

LABEL: 0x20b6
ENG: I replied with a bitter laugh.

LABEL: 0x20da
ENG: "Not like I have anywhere to go home to."

LABEL: 0x21da
JPN: 太い腕に抱えられて、プールサイドにあがったところまではなんとなく覚えている。
ENG: I vaguely remembered a pair of thick arms dragging me up onto the poolside.

LABEL: 0x22d0
JPN: しろはがのぞき込んでいた。
ENG: Shiroha was looking down at my face.

LABEL: 0x25e0
JPN: 「泳ぎの得意なカバでも溺れることはあるらしい」
ENG: "Horses are great at running, but even they fall over sometimes. Swimming's the same way."

LABEL: 0x2a36
JPN: 「俺達がさっさと帰るわけないだろ」
ENG: "As if we'd go home just like that."

LABEL: 0x2a80
JPN: 「倒れた仲間を置いて帰るわけがないだろ」
ENG: "There's no way we'd abandon our collapsed friend."

LABEL: 0x2c14
JPN: 「カバは泳げなくても、流されたりしないだろう……」
ENG: "Even if a horse were to trip, I can't imagine it tumbling through the air..."

LABEL: 0x2c6e
JPN: 「しろははあれ、笑いそうになっただけだと思うぞ」
ENG: "Shiroha was probably just trying not to laugh."

LABEL: 0x2d88
JPN: あ。完全に笑いをこらえてる。
ENG: Ah. Yeah, she's totally trying not to laugh.

LABEL: 0x2f36
JPN: 「小学校のプールで溺れる水泳部として、噂はもちきりよ」
ENG: "The whole town's talking about how a swim club member almost drowned in the elementary school's pool."

LABEL: 0x2fb4
JPN: 「最近あまり泳いでなかったんで、脚がつったんですよ」
ENG: "It's been a while since I last swam, and my leg cramped up."

LABEL: 0x32ec
JPN: しろはが謝っていたのは、俺に対して、不吉な予知をしてしまったから？
ENG: Did Shiroha apologize because she foretold my misfortune?

LABEL: 0x333e
JPN: 俺が溺れたのを自分のせいみたいに思っているんだろうか。
ENG: Maybe she was blaming herself for the fact that I almost drowned.

LABEL: 0x3384
JPN: いつから、彼女はあんな風なんだろう。
ENG: How long has she been that way?

LABEL: 0x33b8
JPN: いつから、ああやって、誰かに謝っていたんだろう。
ENG: How long has she been apologizing for things that aren't her fault at all?
